fi.zudoku.hydraulic.domain.huffman.data

Class HuffmanTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.zudoku.hydraulic.domain.huffman.data.HuffmanTree

  • public class HuffmanTree
extends java.lang.Object
    This represents a complete Huffman tree. This class contains a reference to the root node of the tree. it also has a binary tree to quickly find leafs that we need for compression
